data.label: Identifier
data.formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]] & IF(NOT(Crops[[#This Row],[Variety]] = "General"), " (" & Crops[[#This Row],[Variety]] &")", "") & " - " & Crops[[#This Row],[Product]] & " " & Crops[[#This Row],[Seeds Per Planting]] & "X" & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[CACA]], " ext","")) & " | " & Crops[[#This Row],[Growing Structure]] & " " & Crops[[#This Row],[Planting Method]] & " " & Crops[[#This Row],[Seasons]]

data.label: Audited?
data.formula: =IFERROR(IF(ISNUMBER(MATCH(Crops[[#This Row],[Identifier]],BedPlan[Crop], 0)), TRUE, FALSE), FALSE)

data.label: In Plan
data.formula: =IFERROR(IF(ISNUMBER(MATCH(Crops[[#This Row],[Identifier]],BedPlan[Crop], 0)), TRUE, FALSE), FALSE)

data.label: Common Name
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]

data.label: Planting Method
data.formula: =IF(OR(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]="",Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]=0), "DS","TP")

data.label: Seasons
data.formula: = IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Sp]], "Sp", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Su]], "Su", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Fa]], "Fa", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Wi]], "Wi", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[OW]], "Ow","")

data.label: Plantings Per Bed
data.formula: =IFERROR(12/Crops[[#This Row],[Spacing]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Rows]]*BedLength,"")

data.label: Safety Factor
data.formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Safety Factor]]="",PlantingSafetyFactor,Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Safety Factor]])

data.label: Seeds Per Bed
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Seeds Per Planting]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Seeding Factor]],"")

data.label: Days to Germination
data.formula: =_xlfn.FLOOR.MATH(IFERROR(AVERAGE(Crops[[#This Row],[DTG Lower]:[DTG Upper]]),0))

data.label: Days in Cells
data.formula: =SUM(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Days]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Days]])

data.label: DTM
data.formula: =IFERROR(_xlfn.FLOOR.MATH(AVERAGE(Crops[[#This Row],[DTM Lower]:[DTM Upper]])),"")

data.label: Harvest window
data.formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Harvests]]-1)*Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]+7

data.label: Days In Field
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[STH]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Harvest window]]

data.label: Tray 1 Count
data.formula: =IFERROR(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Days]]=0,"",Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Size]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]),"")

data.label: Tray 2 Count
data.formula: =IFERROR(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]]=0,"",Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Size]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]),"")

data.label: Tray 3 Days
data.formula: =IF(NOT(ISBLANK(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]])), Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells Old]]-SUM(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Days]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]]), "")

data.label: Tray 3 Count
data.formula: =IFERROR(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Days]]=0,"",Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]),"")

data.label: Units Per Harvest
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Harvests]]

data.label: Harvests
data.formula: =28/Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]

data.label: Holding Window
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[Holding Period])

data.label: Custom Yield Per Bed
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Units Per Harvest]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Harvests]]

data.label: Rough Wholesale Price
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Price]]*0.6

data.label: Direct Revenue Per Bed
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Price]]

data.label: Extended Harvest
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Harvests]]>1

data.label: Direct Revenue Per Bed Day
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]],-1)

data.label: Direct Revenue Per Acre Year
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed Day]]*GrowingDays*BedsPerAcre,"")

data.label: Target Sewing Date
data.formula: =LastFrostDate-5*Crops[[#This Row],[Sewing Rel Last Frost]]

data.label: Target Field Date
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Target Sewing Date]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]

data.label: Target Harvest Data
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Target Sewing Date]]+Crops[[#This Row],[STH]]

data.label: Target End of Harvest
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Target Harvest Data]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Harvest window]]

data.label: Bed Prep
data.formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Transplanting]]>0, 2, 3)*BedLength/StandardBedLength

data.label: Seeding Trays
data.formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]<=0,0,Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/StartsPerHourSeeding+Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Count]]*5/60)

data.label: Potting Up
data.formula: =IF(ISBLANK(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]]),0,Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/UpPottingPerHour)+IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Days]]="",0,Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/UpPottingPerHour)

data.label: Start Irrigation
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Count]]/HomeStartFlatIrrigationPerHour,0)*Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]/DaysBetweenStartIrrigation

data.label: Start Transport
data.formula: =0.5/16*MAX(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Count]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Count]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Count]])

data.label: Transplanting
data.formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]>0,IF(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]]>0,Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]],IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Size]]>0,Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Size]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Size]]))<=18,LargeTransplantTime,SmallTransplantTime)*Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]],0)

data.label: Trellising
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Trellis Type]],TrellisMethods[Trellis Type],TrellisMethods[Hours],0,0)

data.label: Direct Seeding
data.formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]<=0,Crops[[#This Row],[Rows]]*1/10,0)*BedLength/50

data.label: Install Row Cover
data.formula: =IF(OR(ISBLANK(Crops[[#This Row],[Row Cover]]),Crops[[#This Row],[Row Cover]]="None"),0,1)*BedLength/50

data.label: Weeding
data.formula: =HoursPerWeedingPass*Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]]/14*Crops[[#This Row],[Rows]]+1*BedLength/50

data.label: Market & Sell
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Marketing (hr)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed]]/2000

data.label: Harvest
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Harvest (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Bunch
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Bunch (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Haul
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Haul (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Wash
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Wash (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Condition
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Condition (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Trim
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Trim (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Pack
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Pack (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Clean
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Clean (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Rehandle
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Rehandle (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Market Transport
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Market Transport (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

data.label: Revenue - Copy
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]

data.label: Direct Time
data.formula: =_xlfn.AGGREGATE(9,6,Crops[[#This Row],[Bed Prep]:[Remove Crop Residue]])

data.label: Wholesale Time
data.formula: =_xlfn.AGGREGATE(9,6,Crops[[#This Row],[Bed Prep]:[Remove Crop Residue]])-0.75*Crops[[#This Row],[Market & Sell]]

data.label: Revenue Per Hour
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]

data.label: Packaging Costs
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[Packaging Cost])*(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[Units Per Pack]))

data.label: Direct Revenue Per Bed2
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Price]],"")

data.label: Direct Labor Cost
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]*LaborRate

data.label: Direct Non-Labor Cost
data.formula: =SUM(Crops[[#This Row],[Irrigation Cost]])

data.label: Direct Total Cost
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Labor Cost]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Non-Labor Cost]]

data.label: Direct Profit
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Total Cost]]

data.label: Direct Profit Per Acre
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Profit]]*BedsPerAcre

data.label: Direct Profit Per Acre Year
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Profit]]*BedsPerAcre*GrowingDays/Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]]

data.label: Direct Profit Per Bed Day
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Profit]]/MIN(Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]],GrowingDays)

data.label: Direct Labor Per Acre
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]] * BedsPerAcre

data.label: Direct Profit Per Owner Labor Hour
data.formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Non-Labor Cost]])/Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]

data.label: Wholesale Revenue Per Bed
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Rough Wholesale Price]],"")

data.label: Wholesale Labor Cost
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Time]]*LaborRate

data.label: Wholesale Non-Labor Cost
data.formula: =SUM(Crops[[#This Row],[Packaging Costs]:[Irrigation Cost]])

data.label: Wholesale Total Cost
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Labor Cost]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Non-Labor Cost]]

data.label: Wholesale Profit
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Revenue Per Bed]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Total Cost]]

data.label: Wholesale Profit Per Acre
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Profit]]*BedsPerAcre

data.label: Wholesale Profit Per Acre Year
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Profit]]*BedsPerAcre*GrowingDays/Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]]

data.label: Wholesale Labor Per Acre
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Time]] * BedsPerAcre

data.label: Wholesale Profit Per Bed Day
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Profit]]/MIN(Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]],GrowingDays)

data.label: Wholesale Profit Per Owner Labor Hour
data.formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Revenue Per Bed]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Non-Labor Cost]])/Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]

data.label: Packaging Percent
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Packaging Costs]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Revenue Per Bed]]

data.label: ProductIndex
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]]

data.label: ProductTarget
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[Target])

data.label: Bed Yield
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]

data.label: Units Per Weekly Harvest
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Units Per Harvest]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]*7

data.label: CSA Portions
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])

data.label: CSA Portions Per Week
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Units Per Harvest]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]*7/_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])

data.label: CSA %
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Portions Per Week]]/CSAMembers

data.label: Propduction Weeks
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Harvests]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]/7

data.label: CSA Need
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Need])

data.label: CSA Times
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Times])

data.label: CSA Harvests
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/(Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Need]]*(_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])*CSAMembers))

data.label: CSA Beds
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])*CSAMembers*Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Need]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]

data.label: CSA Bed Days
data.formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]]*Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Beds]],"")

data.label: Planned CSA Bed Days
data.formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Bed Days]]*#REF!

data.label: Code
data.formula: =UPPER(LEFT(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Crop]],3))

data.label: Display Width
data.formula: =MAX(BedPlan[[#This Row],['# Of Beds]],0.5)

data.label: Start Date
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned Greenhouse Start Date]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned Greenhouse Start Date]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned TP or DS Date]])

data.label: Planned Greenhouse Start Date
data.formula: =IF(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]=0,"",IFERROR(_xlfn.XLOOKUP(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Follows Crop]],BedPlan[Identifier],BedPlan[Expected End of Harvest]) + 1+BedPlan[[#This Row],[Follow Offset]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Fixed Field Start Date]])-BedPlan[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]])

data.label: Greenhouse Start Date
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Greenhouse Date]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Greenhouse Date]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned Greenhouse Start Date]])

data.label: Fixed Field Start Date
data.formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Crop]],Crops[Identifier],Crops[Target Field Date])

data.label: Planned TP or DS Date
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Greenhouse Date]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Greenhouse Date]]+BedPlan[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]],IFERROR(_xlfn.XLOOKUP(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Follows Crop]],BedPlan[Identifier],BedPlan[Expected End of Harvest]) + 1+BedPlan[[#This Row],[Follow Offset]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Fixed Field Start Date]]))

data.label: In Ground Days Late
data.formula: =BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]]-BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned TP or DS Date]]

data.label: TP or DS Date
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned TP or DS Date]])

data.label: Expected Beginning of Harvest
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Greenhouse Start Date]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Greenhouse Start Date]]+BedPlan[[#This Row],[DTM]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[TP or DS Date]]+BedPlan[[#This Row],[DTM]])

data.label: Beginning of Harvest
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Beginning of Harvest]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Beginning of Harvest]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected Beginning of Harvest]])

data.label: Expected End of Harvest
data.formula: =BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected Beginning of Harvest]]+BedPlan[[#This Row],[Harvest Window]]+BedPlan[[#This Row],[Additional Days of Harvest]]

data.label: August Harvest
data.formula: =IF(AND( BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected End of Harvest]] >= DATE(2025, 8, 1), BedPlan[[#This Row],[Beginning of Harvest]] <= DATE(2025, 8, 31) ), TRUE, FALSE)

data.label: End of Harvest
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual End of Harvest]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual End of Harvest]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected End of Harvest]])

data.label: Seeding Done
data.formula: =OR(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual Greenhouse Date]]),ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]]))

data.label: Transplant Done
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned Greenhouse Start Date]]),OR(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Failed]]),"-")

data.label: Harvest Done
data.formula: =OR(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual End of Harvest]]),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Failed]])

data.label: Crop Done
data.formula: =OR(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Harvest Done]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Failed]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Name]]="Tarp")

data.label: Broadfork Date
data.formula: =IF(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Broadfork]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]],"")

data.label: Tilther Date
data.formula: =IF(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Tilther]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]],"")

data.label: Amend Date
data.formula: =IF(NOT(ISBLANK(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Amend]])),BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]],"")

data.label: Row Cover Date
data.formula: =IF(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Row Cover]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Actual TP or DS Date]],"")

data.label: DS/TP
data.formula: =IF(ISNUMBER(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Planned Greenhouse Start Date]]),"TP","DS")

data.label: Full Bed Equivalent
data.formula: =BedPlan[[#This Row],['# Of Beds]]

data.label: Chart Index
data.formula: =MATCH(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Crop]],Crops[Identifier],FALSE)

data.label: Days Until Harvest
data.formula: =BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected Beginning of Harvest]]-DATE(2023,1,1)

data.label: True Harvest Window
data.formula: =BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected End of Harvest]]-BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected Beginning of Harvest]]
=_xlfn.TEXTJOIN(CHAR(10),FALSE,BedPlan[[#This Row],[Name]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Variety]],BedPlan[[#This Row],[Company]])

data.label: Harvest Days January 2025
data.formula: =MAX( 0, MIN(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected End of Harvest]], EOMONTH(CK$4, 0)) - MAX(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Beginning of Harvest]], CK$4) + 1 )

data.label: Harvest Days March 2026
data.formula: =MAX( 0, MIN(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected End of Harvest]], EOMONTH(CY$4, 0)) - MAX(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Beginning of Harvest]], CY$4) + 1 )

data.label: Harvest Days July 2026
data.formula: =MAX( 0, MIN(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Expected End of Harvest]], EOMONTH(DC$4, 0)) - MAX(BedPlan[[#This Row],[Beginning of Harvest]], DC$4) + 1 )

data.label: Harvest Days August 2026
